    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1872-06-25T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1872-06-25T00:00:00-05:00" n="250"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d250">
                <head>No. 115.<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Davis</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Fish</persName>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Geneva</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1872-06-25">
                            <hi rend="italic">June</hi> 25, 1872</date>. (Received at 8
                        p.m.)</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Counsel write me regarding the statement sent Schenck for you to-day:</p>
                <p>We concur in the form of communication to the Tribunal of the action of our
                    Government which you propose to make.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>DAVIS.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
